    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single exception (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted based on COU risk analysis: model risk level 3 with medium model influence and medium decision consequence. The sub-threshold factor is documented and does not invalidate the overall credibility assessment. FEA predictions of all three QoIs fall within the 10% acceptance bound with E/uval well below 1.96. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
